Package com.microblink.entities.recognizers.blinkcard

Class BlinkCardRecognizer.VerificationConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microblink.entities.recognizers.blinkcard.BlinkCardRecognizer.VerificationConstants
  • Enclosing class:
    BlinkCardRecognizer
    public static final class BlinkCardRecognizer.VerificationConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    Constants used for building JSON for the verification service, in case when result fields can be edited and/or inserted. Constants are used to match edited/inserted fields with the original fields.
